<figureCitation box="[1186,1258,436,457]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="5.[126,170,2075,2096]" captionTargetBox="[130,1460,698,2014]" captionTargetId="figure-218@5.[103,1496,671,2014]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figs. 11–13. Hercostomus brevicornis, new species, male: 11, antenna; 12, male genitalia; 13, cercus. iel, inner epandrial lobe; oel, outer epandrial lobe." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5339235" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5339235/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="18">Fig. 12</figureCitation>
) ................................ .................................................... 
